      <div class="highlight highlight-green">
        <strong>Monthly workflow:</strong> Salary arrives → transfer portion to Indodax → buy USDT → transfer to Binance → buy your chosen assets. This takes about 15 minutes once set up. Automate what you can.
      </div>
